  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trust Fund in Support of Victims of Sexual Exploitation and Abuse / voluntary contribution 2017</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="FI">YK:n seksuaalisen hyv&#xE4;ksik&#xE4;yt&#xF6;n uhreja tukeva rahasto / vapaaehtoinen avustus 2017</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FI">2016 YK:n p&#xE4;&#xE4;sihteeri perusti rahaston (Trust Fund in Support of Victims of Sexual Exploitation and Abuse) jonka kautta rahoitetaan seksuaalisen hyv&#xE4;ksik&#xE4;yt&#xF6;n uhreille tarjottavia palveluja ja tukea.  Rahasto on osa aloitteita jotka YK:n p&#xE4;&#xE4;sihteeri
 on tehnyt vastatakseen YK-j&#xE4;rjestelm&#xE4;ss&#xE4; esiintyneeseen seksuaaliseen hyv&#xE4;ksik&#xE4;ytt&#xF6;&#xF6;n. YK on l&#xE4;hestynyt j&#xE4;senmaita pyyt&#xE4;en vapaaehtoisia kontribuutioita rahastoon.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In 2016 the Secretary-General established a Trust Fund (Trust Fund in Support of Victims of Sexual Exploitation and Abuse) in order to support the provision of services to support and assist victims of sexual exploitation and abuse. The Trust Fund is part 
of initiatives by the UN SG to combat sexual exploitation and abuse in the UN system. UN has approached Member States and asked for voluntary contributions to the Fund.</narrative>
  </description>
